# Subnet Research — API Keys
#
# BEFORE creating a .env here, check if these keys already exist elsewhere:
#   - chain-metrics/.env  (TAOSTATS_API_KEY)
#   - desearch/.env       (DESEARCH_API_KEY)
#   - workspace root .env (either key)
# The script scans all sibling skill directories and the workspace root automatically.
# If the keys are already there, you do NOT need this file.
#
# Only create a .env here if you want a self-contained setup or don't have these
# skills installed. To get keys:
#   TAOSTATS_API_KEY — free at https://dash.taostats.io
#   DESEARCH_API_KEY — free at https://desearch.ai
#
# cp .env.example .env  then fill in the values below.

TAOSTATS_API_KEY=
DESEARCH_API_KEY=
